						               													<description>In Drako's Adventure each player takes on the role of Drako (in different player colors) and heads out for some adventures to find the sacred grail of meatballs!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The game is a race to get to the meatballs at the end of the map and players draft action cards and program them to walk, run, jump, fly and flamebreath in the race to be the first pet dragon to make it to the end!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;There's of course obstacles to be faced with on the map, a menhir, a puddle of water or mud or a scary Elk! To make things even harder there's also vikings at some spots on the map, and since Drako loves vikings he just have to stop and admire the mighty (but bored) viking for a bit and so the player loses one of their cards in their programming.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;It's also risky to be in the lead, the other dragons might breath fire and hit you wich will also result in a lost card in the programming. Also look out for bad weather as a storm cloud could stop you from flying!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;To boost your movement you can eat a meatball that you brought to the adventure or found on the way through some meatball bush or meatball tree!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Whoever can handle their pet dragon the best and make it to the end first will get all them juicy meatballs and be the winner of Drako's Adventure.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the designer&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
